<plot>An unusual journey on a tramway. A brief encounter between an old lady and a 12-year-old third-generation North African kid, in Brussels. From buried wishes to nostalgia, a bond is born. On this empty tramway, the lady tells the kid a story. The story of a man who died of not making his dreams come true. What will remain of this life lesson ?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?669448</url></doc>
